Ctrl + b then d
Disconnect from current session

Ctrl + b then %
Splits session/pane horizontaly, new pane

Ctrl + b then "
Slits session/pane vertically, new pane

Ctrl + b then directional keys
Move between panes

Ctrl + b then q
Shows the panes indexes

Ctrl + b then q <numbers>
jumps to the panes with index number

Ctrl + b then hold Ctrl + directional arrows
resizes the pane

Ctrl + b then c
New window

Ctrl + b then n
Move to the window to the left

Ctrl + b then ,
Rename the current window

Ctrl + b then w
Shows overview of all, you can jump to a specific one

Ctrl + b then w
Then Ctrl + b then x
Asks you whether you want to kill this

Ctrl + b then x
Asks you whether you want to kill the current pane

Ctrl + b then &
Kill the whole window

Ctrl + b then [
Enters the copy mode
Hit space key, then copy
Then hit enter, its in the copy buffer

Ctrl + b then ]
paste
